      "role": "user",
      "content": "so i was at dinner with my cousin tonight and i swear i could tell exactly when he was lying about where he was last night. his voice didn't sound different in words but the actual frequency felt... wrong. like there was this weird vibration or dissonance that shouldn't be there. have you ever heard of people being able to sense that kind of thing?",
